com.codename1.rad.nodes

Class SectionNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.rad.models.Attribute<T>
      • com.codename1.rad.nodes.Node
        • com.codename1.rad.nodes.SectionNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<FieldNode>

    public class SectionNode
extends Node
implements Iterable<FieldNode>

    Encapsulates a section of a Form. FormNodes can contain multiple sections (SectionNode).

    Supported Attributes

    1. Label - A label/heading for the section.

    2. Description - A description for the section. Will be rendered in a HelpButton.

    3. Columns - The number of columns in this section.

    4. FieldNode - Can contain multiple fields. These are the fields that should be rendered as a part of this section.

    5. ActionsNode - Can contain multiple ActionsNode nodes to inject buttons and menus in various positions of the section.

      1. Categories include ActionCategories.OVERFLOW_MENU, ActionCategories.TOP_LEFT_MENU, ActionCategories.TOP_RIGHT_MENU, ActionCategories.BOTTOM_LEFT_MENU, ActionCategories.BOTTOM_RIGHT_MENU.

    shannah
